Carrier Line Pricing Locality Code

Code denoting the carrier-specific locality used for pricing the service for this line item on the carrier claim (non-DMERC). Source: https://bluebutton.cms.gov/resources/variables/carrlineprcnglcltycd

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include all codes defined in https://bluebutton.cms.gov/assets/ig/CodeSystem-carr-line-prcng-lclty-cd
